OL,3,CMP's appeal after girl, 17, stabbed in
OL,4,C'traumatic and life changing' event
OL,6,FA man's been arrested after a 17 year
OL,7,Fold girl was stabbed in the neck in
OL,8,FLancashire.
OL,10,FShe's being treated in hospital but
OL,11,Fpolice say her injuries are not life
OL,12,Fthreatening.
OL,14,FThe man, who's 30, is being held on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of attempted murder.
OL,17,FThe incident happened in Wood Street,
OL,18,FBrierfield, around 3pm on Friday June
OL,19,F12.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
