OL,3,CMP's appeal after girl, 17, stabbed in
OL,4,C'traumatic and life changing' event
OL,6,FThe MP for Burnley, Oliver Ryan,
OL,7,Fdescribed it as traumatic and life
OL,8,Fchanging and says it will shock and
OL,9,Fhorrify everyone in the area.
OL,11,FIn a statement on social media he
OL,12,Furged people not to speculate about
OL,13,Fwhat had happened and called for the
OL,14,Fcommunity to 'stick to known facts'.
OL,16,FPolice say extra patrols will be in
OL,17,Fthe area over the weekend to provide
OL,18,Freassurance.
